text: Anna Kindy (born 14 August 1962) is a Canadian freestyle skier. She was born in Montreal, Quebec. She competed at the 1992 Winter Olympics, in women's moguls. == References == == External links == * Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian female freestyle skiers Category:Olympic freestyle skiers of Canada Category:Freestyle skiers at the 1992 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Montreal
